Deploying Dwayne Johnson=E2=80=99s =E2=80=98Red One=E2=80=99 to Prime
Video after only 27 days has angered the theatrical industry and raised a p=
ertinent question that will define this next hybrid era: Can Amazon leverag=
e movie theaters more than theaters can leverage Amazon?

Matthew Belloni ( https://puck.news/author/matthew-belloni/?utm_campaign=3D=
